default&#xa0;default10.1.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIn answering this question it is important to bear in mind what the Government itself says about these 
defaultforecast
defaults
default:
default “
defaultThe NTM Road Traffic Forecasts should not be viewed as what we think will actually happen in the future, or what we want the future to look like. The forecasts are what may happen, based on: 
defaultOur current understanding of how people make travel c
defaulthoices
default; 
defaultThe expected path of key drivers of travel demand
default; 
defaultAssuming no change in government policy beyond that already announced
